Subject: access information center
Description:
HI i updated stealth audit to the latest version which now its Netwrix enterprise. 
im looking to use Access information center but i guess it dosent work now with the new version. how can i get the same data i use to get from access information center?
What_We_Know__c: Customer upgraded NEA but did not upgrade AIC and now AIC is not working with a 500 error.
Next_Steps__c: Customer is reviewing upgrade option and will let me know how he would like to proceed.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
AIC is no longer working after upgrading NEA.

Cause
AIC was not upgraded along side NEA which it should be.

Resolution
Upgrade of AIC resolved the situation and restored AIC.
